{"data":{"wordpressPage":{"title":"HXL postcards (version 1.0)","content":"<p>The <cite>HXL Postcards</cite> provide an overview of the HXL standard in a 4×6 inch (10×15 cm) format, convenient for quick-reference use in the field.  We will be printing and distributing these cards to humanitarian organisations in early 2016. The following languages are currently available in PDF format: <a href=\"#en\">English</a>, <a href=\"#fr\">French (français)</a>, <a href=\"#ar\">Arabic (اللغة العربية)</a>, and <a href=\"#es\">Spanish (español)</a>.</p>\n<section id=\"en\" class=\"postcard-preview\">\n<h2>English</h2>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-en.pdf\"><br />\nDownload English postcard (PDF)<br /><img src=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-en-0.jpg\" alt=\"Thumbnail of front of English-language HXL postcard\" /><img src=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-en-1.jpg\" alt=\"Thumbnail of back of English-language HXL postcard\" /><br />\n</a><br />\n</section>\n<section id=\"fr\" class=\"postcard-preview\">\n<h2>French (français)</h2>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-fr.pdf\"><br />\nDownload French postcard (PDF)<br /><img src=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-fr-0.jpg\" alt=\"Thumbnail of front of French-language HXL postcard\" /><img src=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-fr-1.jpg\" alt=\"Thumbnail of back of French-language HXL postcard\" /><br />\n</a><br />\n</section>\n<section id=\"ar\" class=\"postcard-preview\">\n<h2>Arabic (اللغة العربية)</h2>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-ar.pdf\"><br />\nDownload Arabic postcard (PDF).<br /><img src=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-ar-0.jpg\" alt=\"Thumbnail of front of Arabic-language HXL postcard\" /><img src=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-ar-1.jpg\" alt=\"Thumbnail of back of Arabic-language HXL postcard\" /><br />\n</a><br />\n</section>\n<section id=\"es\" class=\"postcard-preview\">\n<h2>Spanish (español)</h2>\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-es.pdf\"><br />\nDownload Spanish postcard (PDF)<br /><img src=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-es-0.jpg\" alt=\"Thumbnail of front of Spanish-language HXL postcard\" /><img src=\"http://hxl2.local/wp-content/uploads/hxl-postcard-es-1.jpg\" alt=\"Thumbnail of back of Spanish-language HXL postcard\" /><br />\n</a><br />\n</section>\n"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Gatsby Default Starter"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"97d90013-5cb6-56e7-8d16-bab1dcc06f37"}}